Splitting the teams, the current team size is too large.
methodology
split big teams already
Sence that the whole team responsible for products quality
More deeply planing, preventing risks, finding connections between teams
Automation
More data shared how the internal design is made
Realistic planning and not taking tasks which aren't in the sprint
